00:00:53.080 --> 00:01:00.500
 And he, again, therefore, also the Dhamma Kaya Buddha, the Samad Bhadara,

00:01:00.500 --> 00:01:04.000
 when he gave this teaching, on the Konsi Jaipur.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:10.080
 The Konsi Jaipur is named the Bodhijata king of all creations.

00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:13.480
 So that is what, really, because it's so important.

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:18.600
 And that Dzogchen itself is the embodiment of the Bodhijata.

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:22.480
 And then Bodhijata, of course, you all know there's two Bodhijata,

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:26.680
 which is known as the outreaching Bodhijata in a relative level.

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:31.120
 And then the Bodhijata, which is free from the attachment and grasping,

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:34.880
 and that which is known as then the absolute Bodhijata in one way.

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:39.760
 So this Bodhijata of Dzogchen is united together

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:44.360
 with all the separating the absolute and the relative to Bodhijata,

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:47.180
 not going to target it in one single status.

00:01:47.180 --> 00:01:50.760
 And therefore, at the beginning of time, when we meditate in the practice,

00:01:50.760 --> 00:01:54.560
 and Dzogchen practice more kind of focus on the emptiness aspect

00:01:54.560 --> 00:02:00.120
 with true nature, and that's because due to our grasping duality regiment,

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:04.360
 that carried us, like, so long time, life after life,

00:02:04.360 --> 00:02:08.880
 that kind of whoring, grasping, and kind of regiment attitude

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:13.800
 was the mostly kind of like principle factors of the obstacle.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:17.520
 Therefore, immediately teaching kind of tells the emptiness,

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:20.160
 emptiness, kind of emptiness, that teaching.

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:23.120
 But emptiness alone is of course you all know.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:28.520
 And we will all through this, it's not really the true nature itself alone.

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:33.640
 Emptiness, the fullness status, and so what is empty, that is full,

00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:36.080
 and what is full, and that is emptiness.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:41.240
 And in that case, what is empty, that is compassion, or great compassion.

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:44.160
 What is great compassion, and that is emptiness.

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:49.640
 They are united together without any slightly kind of the distinctions

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:52.960
 between them as like even one single here is there,

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:55.760
 between there we can find, completely united.

00:02:55.760 --> 00:03:00.720
 And that is what we should kind of recognizing,

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:04.920
 and kind of re-conforming that view,

00:03:04.920 --> 00:03:08.000
 or that understanding in our heart, in the mind.

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:22.160
 So what we should do is we should think of the same things

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:24.000
 as we have in our mind.

