00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:53.280
 we received our practice at Zouki,

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:55.880
 we should not kind of carry away, again,

00:03:55.880 --> 00:03:58.480
 with the kind of emptiness, attitude,

00:03:58.480 --> 00:04:03.120
 and ignoring all the beauty of that emptiness.

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:06.640
 And then it will kind of, again, become the extreme status.

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:10.120
 And that, for those reasons, repeatedly

00:04:10.120 --> 00:04:14.800
 all those gracious teachers, warned to the practice,

00:04:14.800 --> 00:04:18.160
 then shouldn't fall completely in the kind

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:23.360
 of extreme nihilism or kind of that emptiness, that ditch,

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:25.160
 ditch, or the black hole.

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:27.480
