00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:37.880
 from now, kind of starting to all cooperate

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:39.840
 and target these beautiful things.

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:43.840
 Targeting and practice will make, then, everything beautiful.

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:45.400
 Beginner is beautiful.

