00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:57.360
 the first gracious, first the most important,

00:04:57.360 --> 00:05:02.600
 or first the most famous lineage holder of the Dzogchen

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:04.680
 after Gharap Durya, or the Gharap Durya,

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:07.440
 the most famous disciple you all know,

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:10.960
 the Manjishri Mitra, in a debate called Jambahini.

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:14.680
