00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:18.880
 wrote the commentaries on the Dzogchen teaching renowned,

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:23.200
 which is, as you all know, and which is known as, and then

00:05:23.200 --> 00:05:26.880
 meditating on the bodhicitta, bodhicitta.

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:30.800
 And that was the title of the Dzogchen teaching,

