 that he didn't name any other fancy names to his book,

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:39.400
 the first book of the Dzogchen teaching,

00:05:39.400 --> 00:05:44.640
 only meditating on the bodhicitta, all which

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:52.560
 is a nugget gold liquid from the stone.

